/*------------------------------------------------------------------
MBlue Nav-Style Url-Bar Vista (Ver. 0.5.2)

Author: M.BLUE - Tested on: Firefox 3.5.1 - Last Update: 27.07.2009
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Description:
 1. Transforms the URLBAR/SEARCHBAR and make it like the
    NAV-BUTTONS: same blue background, same buttons and dropmarker.
 2. Make the GO-BUTTON always visible by default, and make it looks
    the same as the Forward-Button (Nav-Buttons), and apply that to
    the SEARCH-BUTTON too.
 3. Skins "FISSION" Progress-Bar.
 4. Skins and combine "CLEAR FIELDS" icons (optional) (*).
 5. Supports Locationbar2 and XMarks.
 6. Supports SMALL and LARGE ICONS.
 7. Highly customizable.
 8. Integrates with the other Nav-Style styles.
 9. Integrates with "Combine Nav-Buttons Vista".

Notes:
-Using other Styles/Extensions/Themes may change some settings,
 making the buttons/textboxes overlap each other.
 If so, don't use those styles, and use the default firefox theme. 

-Works in the Nav-Bar only, small/large icons, no label, no flex.

-If using "Clear Fields" extension, remember to follow the
 instructions below (*).
--------------------------------------------------------------------
*COMBINE "CLEAR FIELDS" ICONS (OPTIONAL):

 This style combines the "Clear Fields" Extension Icons with the
 Url-Bar and Search-Bar. To make it works, you need to place the
 buttons in this order:

 [URLBAR] [CLEAR-ADDRESS]  &  [SEARCHBAR] [CLEAR-SEARCH]

 The icons will auto-combine if everything id done the right way.
--------------------------------------------------------------------
CUSTOMIZING:

 1. TEXT COLOR/SIZE/WEIGHT/OPACITY/ALIGN (DEFAULT & LOCATIONBAR2).
 2. URLBAR/SEARCHBAR BLUE/TRANSPARENT.
 3. URLBAR/SEARCHBAR and NAV-BUTTONS OPACITY.
 4. FISSION-BAR COLOR and OPACITY.
 5. SEARCHBAR WIDTH.

> GO TO BOTTOM OF THE PAGE TO CUSTOMIZE
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Supported Extensions:
 Fission, Clear Fields, Locationbar2, XMarks, Read IT Later.

Integrates with:
 MBlue Combine Nav-Buttons Vista
>MBlue Nav-Style Url-Bar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Buttons Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Tabs Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Statusbar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Throbber Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Bookmarks-Bar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Awesome-Bar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Menubar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Sidebar Vista
 MBlue Nav-Style Sidebar Vista (Downloads, Addons, Extensions)
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Updates:
 27.07.2009 Ver. 0.5.2 = added Read IT Later support
 23.07.2009 Ver. 0.5.1 = added XMarks support, code optimized
 18.07.2009 Ver. 0.5.0 = better FF 3.5 support
 10.07.2009 Ver. 0.4.5 = added FF 3.5 support
 27.01.2009 Ver. 0.4.1 = fixed urlbar
 27.01.2009 Ver. 0.4.0 = added namespace, added support for the
                         Combine Home-Button Vista style, few fixes
 ...
 16.09.2008 Ver. 0.3.0 = lot of fixes, better integration
 ...
 01.08.2008 Ver. 0.2.0 = ready to release
 ...
------------------------------------------------------------------*/



